data.description: Here is a terrific property with a great yard! This traditional brick has many updates including new flooring  and fresh paint throughout, new bathrooms, heat pump, gutter guards and more! This one level living has large rooms and unfinished basement for storage. The primary suite is situated at the back of the home with large full bathroom and access to the back yard were you will find a new deck. The other two bedrooms (one with half bath) and a large full guest bath are just off the living room. Enjoy entertaining family and friends in the back yard under the picnic and pergola. The kitchen has new appliances and lots of cabinets and large island and bar top with serve through for more seating. There is a mudroom from the back door with utility sink and storage. Outdoor fireplace for those cool evenings. Bring your rocking chairs to sit on the covered front porch. There is a workshop for tinkering, garden and outdoor storage and more. The spacious carport has room for parking and there is a paved driveway  for ample parking. This property is just off the 11E that is just minutes from Greeneville and Jonesborough.
